WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=2  | publisher=工商晚報 | date=1979-10-25 | accessdate=2020-05-28|quote= }}</ref>。她曾任《[[欢乐今宵|欢乐今宵]]》的节目主持，与[[戚美珍|戚美珍]]、[[廖安丽|廖安丽]]并称为“欢乐三小花”。擅长演绎娇憨活泼、刁蛮任性的少女角色，曾於多部電視劇中擔任主要角色，包括《[[鹿鼎記_(1984年電視劇)|鹿鼎记]]》的[[和碩恪純長公主|建宁公主]]、《[[雪山飛狐_(1985年電視劇)|雪山飞狐]]》的[[程灵素|程灵素]]及《[[陆小凤之凤舞九天_(1986年电视剧)|陆小凤之凤舞九天]]》的薛冰等。亦曾於1982年獲得[[永恆唱片|永恆唱片]]高層欣賞其歌藝而簽約成為歌手<ref>{{cite news | title=景黛音有突破 簽約成爲歌星 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E6%99%AF%E9%BB%9B%E9%9F%B3&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2FH7zGe%2FKF%2BFAmW5FzaBlcB&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=67&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E6%99%AF%E9%BB%9B%E9%9F%B3%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E6%99%AF%E9%BB%9B%E9%9F%B3%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E6%99%AF%E9%BB%9B%E9%9F%B3%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E6%99%AF%E9%BB%9B%E9%9F%B3%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E6%99%AF%E9%BB%9B%E9%9F%B3%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E6%99%AF%E9%BB%9B%E9%9F%B3%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=4  | publisher=工商晚報 | date=1982-07-19| accessdate=2020-05-28|quote= }}</ref>，且推出個人唱片《[[少女情懷|少女情懷]]》、《香江花月夜》、《[[痴痴不再|痴痴不再]]》。及後，她因操勞過度而患上急性肝炎<ref>{{cite news | title=因患上肝炎休息後復出拍劇集 景黛音覺得不習慣 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E6%99%AF%E9%BB%9B%E9%9F%B3&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E6%99%AF%E9%BB%9B%E9%9F%B3%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E6%99%AF%E9%BB%9B%E9%9F%B3%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E6%99%AF%E9%BB%9B%E9%9F%B3%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E6%99%AF%E9%BB%9B%E9%9F%B3%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E6%99%AF%E9%BB%9B